name: Traditional Painting the Swans and the Turtle #2
description: I made this painting manually with acrylic on canvas by using the sungging technique, and made carefully and thoroughly so it takes a long time. I have to stack the colors from light to dark and I also have to wait for the previous color to dry first. This painting tells of a swan and a turtle who are experiencing a dry season and it is difficult for them to survive. so they started planning to move to the lake under the foot of the mountain.
